# layouts Directory Guide

The [layouts/](mdc:layouts) directory contains layout components for different types of pages:

- [AuthorLayout.tsx](mdc:layouts/AuthorLayout.tsx): Layout for author profile pages.
- [ListLayout.tsx](mdc:layouts/ListLayout.tsx): Layout for listing blog posts or other items.
- [ListLayoutWithTags.tsx](mdc:layouts/ListLayoutWithTags.tsx): List layout with tag filtering support.
- [PostLayout.tsx](mdc:layouts/PostLayout.tsx): Layout for individual blog post pages.

Use these layouts to wrap content and provide consistent structure across the site.
